lead_paragraph: Wallabies back Christian Lealiifano was awarded the ACT Brumbies' top prize at an emotional club function on Friday as he continues his battle against leukaemia.

headline.print_headline: Cancer Patient Lealiifano Awarded Top Brumbies Prize
